name: Lesley Welte
description:
I’m looking to find a good man to build a serious relationship.
Someone to share my thoughts and dreams with. If that’s you keep reading.
If you’re looking for a ONS, FWB or are involved then please feel free to leave my post.
I’m a loyal, smart and caring woman who loves a good laugh.
I’m 45 years old and enjoy a date night out just as much as a quiet evening at home with a good movie and some cuddling.
